Package: SteadyStateBVAR
Title: Steady State Bayesian Vector Autoregression
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person("Mark", "Becker", , "mark.jw.becker@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Estimation of Bayesian Vector Autoregression (BVAR) models
    with steady-state priors using Stan. Supports homoscedastic models
    and stochastic volatility specifications with Random Walk or AR(1)
    processes.
